      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with its high-revving 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example maintains its mechanical integrity with a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes VANOS servicing and a subframe inspection, ensuring the chassis dynamics remain sharp. Finished in Carbon Black, the exterior shows honest wear consistent with its enthusiast-driven history, while the interior retains its ergonomic focus. A robust platform for those who value visceral feedback and linear power delivery over concours perfection.",
